profile:
ONSITE SPECIALTY TOOLMAKERS AND HANDYMAN SERVICES INC. was created to allow anyone access to the highest levels of toolmakers and their handyman abilities. 

  
We offer a multiple trade solution to manufacturing downtime available to anyone, anywhere on their premises. Our skills allow us to design, customize, modify and repair any type of commercial, industrial and residential equipment and tooling.

Our certified tradesmen can accomplish the repair and modification of equipment in a matter of hours on location rather than costly shipping and downtime. Our level of tooling and automation knowledge combined with precision TIG welding skills allow us to perform repairs and modifications to many types of tooling, secondary equipment, fixtures and quality assurance gauges.

Check us out online and follow us on Twitter  @onsitetoolmaker @precisewelding
